OL,5, Major UK businesses are lining up to   
OL,6, offer jobs to Ukrainian refugees when  
OL,7, they start to arrive in the UK.        
OL,9,FA group of more than 45 large          
OL,10,Fbusinesses is pressing the government  
OL,11,Fto make it easier for those driven out 
OL,12,Fby Russia's invasion to come to the UK.
OL,14,FMarks & Spencer, Asos, Lush and        
OL,15,Frecruitment giant Robert Walters are   
OL,16,Fsome of the firms involved.            
OL,18,FThe government has been criticised over
OL,19,Fthe speed and scale of its response to 
OL,20,Fthe Ukraine refugee crisis.            
